 straints.\nPlan:\n- Warm-up: 8 min bike\, dynamic hamstrings\, glute brid
 ges\, ankle mobility\, and light hinge ramp sets.\n- Romanian deadlift: 2
 -3 x 6-8.\n- Hip thrust or glute bridge: 3 x 8-12.\n- Front-foot elevated
  split squat: 3 x 8-10 per leg\, knee tracking cleanly.\n- Seated or lyin
