SUMMARY:Controlled Hill Sprints + Mobility
DESCRIPTION:Macros: 3250 kcal\, 160 g protein\, 445 g carbs\, 90 g fat\nCa
 tegory: sprint\nRun volume: 3 km\nAdjustments:\n- Adjusted for schedule c
 onstraints.\nPlan:\n- Warm-up jog: 3 km total including cooldown\, all ea
 sy.\n- Dynamic drills: leg swings\, A-skips\, ankling\, high knees\, and 
 3 relaxed strides.\n- Hill sprints: 4 x 10-12 sec uphill at powerful but 
 controlled effort\; full walk-back recovery.\n- Stop the sprint set if me
 chanics get sloppy or knees feel sharp.\n- Accessory option: farmer carri
 es 4 x 30-40 m and ab wheel 3 x 6-10.\n- Fueling: have carbs before the s
 ession and hydrate with electrolytes if sleep was poor.\n- Keep this sess
 ion flexible: reduce volume by 25-40% before adding intensity.
