SUMMARY:Easy Longer Aerobic Run
DESCRIPTION:Macros: 3250 kcal\, 160 g protein\, 445 g carbs\, 90 g fat\nCa
 tegory: long_run\nRun volume: 8 km\nAdjustments:\n- Adjusted for schedule
  constraints.\nPlan:\n- Easy longer run: 8 km at conversational effort\, 
 roughly 5:15-5:55/km.\n- This is not a race. Keep the final 2 km controll
 ed unless recovery feels excellent.\n- Post-run: protein plus a large car
 b meal within 2 hours.\n- Mobility: calves\, quads\, hip flexors\, and ge
 ntle knee-friendly range work.\n- Fueling: eat carbs the night before and
  before the run\; add electrolytes if warm.\n- Keep this session flexible
 : reduce volume by 25-40% before adding intensity.
